{"tid":659862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今次瀨嘢了","createTime":"2018-05-10T08:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T09:39:55.000Z","uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c377505542783909f35d479909480f9c6a92a24","tid":659862,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"尋晚去條女屋企食飯<br />\n佢阿媽醃咗條魚煎，問我好唔好食，我話落鹽重手咗<br />\n碟鮑魚佢話用咗好多時間炆，我話頭先食嗰隻OK，呢隻鹹咗D<br />\n嗰刻我都隱約覺得伯母笑容有少少凝固咗<br />\n同條女唔知點解睥住我<br />\n食完飯伯母無留我，我就返咗屋企了<br />\n當我返到屋企思前想後<br />\n知道金翅仆街鳥<br />\n而家點算好？"},{"pid":"4de1de7f29c4b2a78c3effc8672c376ca99082da","tid":659862,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/161603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F161603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f569648f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d20200441e7813a30ba44fed472d88e92c45f35b","tid":659862,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"molamola 跪玻璃啦"},{"pid":"f6f483df077d8835a216268410f9b949ff9b1724","tid":659862,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"買紥玫瑰送比佢老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d8f277acd9f391372787e811a9e296b121cd69","tid":659862,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"下次上佢屋企，罰自己一路奶佢老母隻鮑魚一路話好味"},{"pid":"5b8390d1a3de122ae69d6ac81631181952fc6a8b","tid":659862,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"幾歲呀樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見家長客套說話都唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做戲都要做啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=